Digital Signage System
----------------------

The aim of this project, is to provide a simple Digital Signage Solution for use on Linux-based clients.

Information is displayed as a 'Board', which can contain various forms of information, from Static Notifications, to Media streams.

Current Features:

 * Allow use of multiple Boards.
 * BBC iPlayer Integration
 * Allow streaming of Video/Sound for various board/slides.
 * Built-in Weather API Included supports feeds from WorldWeatherOnline.com
 * Scaling support for various display types (Default 16:9)
 * WebUI Preview System (required Apache support and use of orbital_wui)
